count(word)

my_db <- dbConnect(RSQLite::SQLite(), ":memory:")

query_top5_delay <- "
SELECT carrier, AVG(arr_delay) AS avg_arr_delay
FROM flights
GROUP BY carrier
ORDER BY avg_arr_delay DESC
LIMIT 10
"

query_ewr <- "
WITH ewr_flights AS (
SELECT flight, carrier, dep_delay, arr_delay
FROM flights
WHERE origin = 'EWR'
),
avg_arr AS (
SELECT AVG(arr_delay) AS avg_arr_delay
FROM ewr_flights
)
SELECT f.flight, f.carrier, f.dep_delay, f.arr_delay
FROM ewr_flights AS f, avg_arr
WHERE f.arr_delay > avg_arr.avg_arr_delay
ORDER BY f.arr_delay DESC
LIMIT 10
"

SELECT f.month, f.day, f.flight, f.carrier, f.dep_delay, f.arr_delay,
f.tailnum, p.model, p.seats
FROM flights AS f
INNER JOIN planes AS p
ON f.tailnum = p.tailnum

) +
